    "body": "I believe this is impossible with the way things work. You see templates in the tile selector. That is painted onto the map which saves those painted tiles per cell. It doesn't know which template you chose. Just like painting a wall. You can't undo the painting with an eraser color or brush. You can just add a new layer of color on top of it.\n"
